        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Paracyatholaimus huanghaiensis sp. nov. (A) Lateral view of female, showing vulva, ovary and egg; (B) lateral view of male head end, showing buccal cavity, amphideal fovea and cephalic setae; (C) lateral view of male pharynx posterior end, showing ventral gland; (D) lateral view of male posterior body part, showing spicules, gubernaculum and precloacal supplements." ;
